description:
Mercury is a Marble Madness-style puzzler/platformer played with liquid balls drawn with special metallic reflection effects to make it look like moving gobs of mercury, hence the game title.


Emulated with PPSSPP 0.9.6. The emulator is Xbox360 controller compatible.


System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher.
nVidia GeForce GT 610 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.
2 Gig of ram or more.
Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.

Extract with 7zip, or winrar.

